Package: tidygapminder
Type: Package
Title: A Set of Functions to Handle Gapminder Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Anicet", "Ebou", email = "anicet.ebou@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Anicet Ebou <anicet.ebou@gmail.com>
Description: A set of functions to handle gapminder datasets. It provides
    useful functions to tidy a bunch or single indice data sheet, and turn it into
    one dataframe.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
